261
00:17:52,867 --> 00:17:54,210
"Heart patient!"

262
00:17:54,700 --> 00:17:57,442
These old folks blackmail one
for the smallest things.

263
00:17:57,633 --> 00:17:59,374
I'm a heart patient!

264
00:17:59,800 --> 00:18:01,438
You're bound to die some day!

265
00:18:01,800 --> 00:18:02,801
Elope with her.

266
00:18:02,867 --> 00:18:05,143
Pack your bags and elope.
I will deal with the rest.

267
00:18:05,200 --> 00:18:07,237
You don't have to create
that kind of scene.

268
00:18:07,800 --> 00:18:09,609
