with everyone's consent.

269
00:18:09,667 --> 00:18:11,044
And it will be a great wedding!

270
00:18:11,133 --> 00:18:12,043
A great wedding.

271
00:18:12,133 --> 00:18:14,807
Anyway, your sugar levels are too high.
- What?

272
00:18:15,567 --> 00:18:18,878
