Right?

275
00:18:26,067 --> 00:18:28,047
The sugar level
will level itself out.

276
00:18:28,467 --> 00:18:31,243
Do you know why I am the top most
caterer in Ahmadabad?

277
00:18:31,633 --> 00:18:34,671
