opened up her bank locker.

284
00:18:46,800 --> 00:18:48,245
I'm sure it doesn't
contain a treasure.

285
00:18:48,333 --> 00:18:50,370
What do you mean?
- Fine, I'll get it. Come on.

286
00:18:50,433 --> 00:18:52,106
Don't forget.
- Alright, I won't.

287
00:19:06,067 --> 00:19:07,705
Hey, Mr. Noticewala!

288
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:09,843
What is this?

289
00:19:09,900 --> 00:19:12,403
My name is not Mr. Noticewala.

290
00:19:12,467 --> 00:19:14,140
I have told you so many times!

291
00:19:14,200 --> 00:19:19,149
My name is Nawab Mehmood
Nazeem Ali Shah Khan Bahadur.

292
00:19:19,200 --> 00:19:20,178
Show some respect.

293
00:19:20,267 --> 00:19:22,213
I asked for your name,
not a long winded address.

294
00:19:22,567 --> 00:19:23,875
Forget it!
What's going on?

295
00:19:23,967 --> 00:19:25,708
Why do you keep handing out
notices for every little thing?

296
00:19:25,767 --> 00:19:27,804
