junk to the side?

297
00:19:27,967 --> 00:19:29,002
Junk?
-Yes!

298
00:19:29,100 --> 00:19:31,102
This is a 1945 car!

299
00:19:31,167 --> 00:19:32,202
It's a vintage car!

300
00:19:32,300 --> 00:19:34,280
