305
00:19:44,867 --> 00:19:46,346
No, I was in the washroom.

306
00:19:47,533 --> 00:19:48,773
In the washroom?

307
00:19:49,167 --> 00:19:51,147
What kind of food do
you guys eat?

308
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:52,508
Washroom?

309
00:19:53,233 --> 00:19:54,541
Uncultured man!

310
00:19:54,867 --> 00:19:58,838
I meant, I was in the bathroom.

311
00:20:00,333 --> 00:20:01,607
Uncultured?

312
00:20:02,333 --> 00:20:04,006
Do you know what jhajharu?

313
00:20:04,933 --> 00:20:06,207
Jhajharu?

314
00:20:06,300 --> 00:20:08,371
Jhajharu?
Do you know what it means?

315
00:20:09,333 --> 00:20:11,677
Bathroom!
Right?

316
00:20:12,900 --> 00:20:13,970
Yes, right.

317
00:20:14,067 --> 00:20:16,741
But, it's not right to keep
handing out these notices.

318
00:20:16,800 --> 00:20:19,371
