with the notice.

319
00:20:19,467 --> 00:20:20,707
You will have to pay that.

320
00:20:22,100 --> 00:20:23,670
I won't pay this.

321
00:20:24,267 --> 00:20:25,803
I will never pay this!

322
00:20:25,900 --> 00:20:27,106
What proof do you have...

323
00:20:27,167 --> 00:20:29,204
...that I scratched that
junked up car of yours?

324
00:20:29,700 --> 00:20:31,145
Want to file a case?
Go ahead!

325
00:20:31,200 --> 00:20:32,372
Go ahead and file a lawsuit!

326
00:20:32,567 --> 00:20:34,808
Why don't you forget it?
Let's go. - Why should I?

327
00:20:34,900 --> 00:20:36,743
He's been issuing notices at
the slightest provocation...

328
00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:38,074
...since 6 months!

329
00:20:38,133 --> 00:20:40,204
If it's such trouble
why did you come to live here?

330
00:20:40,300 --> 00:20:42,143
Go and live in a Muslim
locality. Go on!

331
00:20:42,200 --> 00:20:44,146
Listen...
- Communal discrimination!

332
00:20:44,400 --> 00:20:45,879
This is India!

333
00:20:45,933 --> 00:20:49,005
Under the Constitutional
Law 295 -A...

334
00:20:49,100 --> 00:20:50,738
...and 298...

335
00:20:50,800 --> 00:20:52,711
...I can put you behind bars!

336
00:20:52,767 --> 00:20:55,873
I am not doing to get scared of
these laws and so on!

337
00:20:55,933 --> 00:20:57,606
I am not one to get scared either.
- Yes.

338
00:20:57,700 --> 00:20:59,373
I won't get scared, either!

339
00:20:59,467 --> 00:21:00,707
You listen to me.

340
00:21:00,800 --> 00:21:02,905
Don't try to pull rank
since you're in a majority.

341
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:05,105
This is not going to
work with me.

342
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:07,009
I don't care what
messes you come up with...

343
00:21:07,067 --> 00:21:08,808
...what issues you come up...

344
00:21:08,867 --> 00:21:10,107
...I will get my head cut off,
but I won't bow it!

345
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:13,670
Now, these people can't think
beyond killing or cutting up stuff.

346
00:21:13,733 --> 00:21:16,441
Why are you doing this?
You have to go to the bank.

347
00:21:16,500 --> 00:21:18,343
Let's go!
- Crazy man. - Let's go!

348
00:21:18,433 --> 00:21:19,377
Let's go! Come on!

349
00:21:19,467 --> 00:21:20,946
What on earth!

350
00:21:32,500 --> 00:21:34,537
Ms. Alka! How are you?

351
00:21:34,633 --> 00:21:36,340
Sit, Mr. Dharampal.

352
00:21:36,633 --> 00:21:38,135
I'm fine.

353
00:21:38,233 --> 00:21:39,906
I heard about your mom.

354
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:43,040
Yes, well, I guess age will
have its way.

355
00:21:43,333 --> 00:21:45,074
She was such a pleasant woman!

356
00:21:45,133 --> 00:21:47,113
I still miss her.

357
00:21:47,200 --> 00:21:48,440
She was a nice person.

358
00:21:48,700 --> 00:21:52,477
And she really loved you, too.

359
00:21:52,533 --> 00:21:56,071
No matter what we do, we
can never repay our parents.

360
00:21:57,233 --> 00:21:58,837
Would you like some tea,
coffee, a cold drink?

361
00:21:58,933 --> 00:22:00,674
No, nothing, thanks.
Just the locker, please.

362
00:22:00,767 --> 00:22:02,041
Okay.
- Let's go. - Let's go.

363
00:23:13,567 --> 00:23:16,673
Dad, you look exactly like grandpa.
Right?

364
00:23:16,733 --> 00:23:17,939
No.

365
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:22,012
I think, your dad looks more
like his mom.

366
00:23:22,433 --> 00:23:23,810
Don't you think so?

367
00:23:27,900 --> 00:23:29,811
Dad seems disturbed, doesn't he?

368
00:23:34,500 --> 00:23:36,810
Please make it tasty.
We have elite guests.

369
00:23:37,933 --> 00:23:39,139
He makes kachoris.
- Hmm.

370
00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:40,611
He's a good chef.
- Mm hmm.

371
00:23:40,700 --> 00:23:42,111
He's been at it since
three years.

372
00:23:43,067 --> 00:23:45,104
What's his name?
- Abdul Hameed.

373
00:23:47,167 --> 00:23:50,080
I forgot to tell you.
There's a chef from Surat.

374
00:23:50,133 --> 00:23:52,135
I have called him in, okay?
- Okay.

375
00:23:52,467 --> 00:23:54,310
Sorry, we'll call
you if we need you.

376
00:23:54,367 --> 00:23:55,812
I'll call you.
- Yes, sir.

377
00:23:56,500 --> 00:23:58,343
No use of coming here.

378
00:23:59,700 --> 00:24:00,838
Dharam Bhai.
- Yes?

379
00:24:01,267 --> 00:24:03,247
We have an order for a huge
dinner party.

380
00:24:03,533 --> 00:24:05,843
You have to handle it for
the next few days, please.

381
00:24:05,900 --> 00:24:07,937
Alright, as you wish.

382
00:24:28,800 --> 00:24:31,679
Oh wow!
This is amazing.

383
00:24:33,333 --> 00:24:37,645
Sethji, thank you for
the donation to our orphanage.

384
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:44,472
Alright, Mr. Bhatt.
Tell me. -Yes?

385
00:24:45,500 --> 00:24:50,279
Can you say with complete faith
that the kids who come here...

386
00:24:50,333 --> 00:24:53,109
...you don't reveal
their parents identity?

387
00:24:53,500 --> 00:24:55,446
I am absolutely sure.

388
00:24:55,500 --> 00:24:58,743
We have to be extremely
careful about that.

389
00:24:59,767 --> 00:25:02,748
I can see lots of
old records and files.

390
00:25:02,800 --> 00:25:05,178
It's stacked in here.
We have lots of records.

391
00:25:05,233 --> 00:25:09,375
1965, 1655, 1945, 1960.

392
00:25:09,433 --> 00:25:11,674
