back there? - Yes.

398
00:25:24,867 --> 00:25:27,746
It contains files...

399
00:25:27,800 --> 00:25:29,802
...from 1950 to 1960.

400
00:25:30,333 --> 00:25:31,812
Really? I don't believe it.

401
00:25:31,867 --> 00:25:34,177
If you don't believe it,
I'll fetch them. Wait.

402
00:25:34,434 --> 00:25:36,038
Let me show you this, too.

403
00:25:36,134 --> 00:25:38,341
There are loads of papers in here.

404
00:25:38,400 --> 00:25:41,006
What's the big deal?
Look at this, please.

405
00:25:41,533 --> 00:25:45,845
1955, 1956, 1958.

406
00:25:46,000 --> 00:25:48,776
