409
00:25:55,833 --> 00:25:56,937
not computers.

410
00:25:57,000 --> 00:25:59,002
You press a button and it
says, file not found.

411
00:26:00,600 --> 00:26:02,204
1960...

412
00:26:03,900 --> 00:26:06,312
What immaculate records!

413
00:26:07,133 --> 00:26:10,273
What happened?
- It's a secret.

414
00:26:10,333 --> 00:26:12,142
It's secret!
- That's nice.

415
00:26:12,200 --> 00:26:13,304
It's secret.

416
00:26:13,367 --> 00:26:15,711
No, but...
- No, but it's secret.

417
00:26:15,767 --> 00:26:18,475
I want to see it.
What are you doing?

418
00:26:18,533 --> 00:26:20,103
Hey, let go!

419
00:26:20,300 --> 00:26:22,211
Shailesh, Bhupesh, Nimesh, Aakash!

420
00:26:22,534 --> 00:26:24,138
That file is top secret!
Catch him!

421
00:26:24,200 --> 00:26:25,679
Don't let him go!

422
00:26:28,567 --> 00:26:30,308
Hey, let go!

423
00:26:30,367 --> 00:26:31,869
Oh, God!
- What?

424
00:26:33,267 --> 00:26:36,180
Break the window!
It's top secret! - Get back!

425
00:26:36,267 --> 00:26:37,905
What is this?
Sethji!

426
00:26:37,967 --> 00:26:40,345
Sethji! Give me the file!

427
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:42,346
Give me the file!

428
00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:44,402
Sethji! Please listen to me.

429
00:26:44,500 --> 00:26:45,877
Listen... nab him!

430
00:26:45,933 --> 00:26:47,810
Nab him!

431
00:26:48,467 --> 00:26:50,344
Hey! Shut the door!
- Get back!

432
00:26:50,867 --> 00:26:53,814
Praveen! Catch him!
What did he eat for breakfast?

433
00:26:54,534 --> 00:26:56,673
