440
00:27:15,134 --> 00:27:17,705
What are you doing?
- Sethji, please.

441
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:19,708
Please!

442
00:27:30,033 --> 00:27:31,740
Meer Saukhat Ali.

443
00:27:32,534 --> 00:27:34,309
Muslim!

444
00:27:36,233 --> 00:27:37,337
Muslim!

445
00:29:12,933 --> 00:29:14,207
Remember!

446
00:29:14,300 --> 00:29:16,871
What is true, is right.

447
00:29:38,900 --> 00:29:40,106
What is this, God?

448
00:29:41,533 --> 00:29:43,376
Why did you create this mess?

449
00:29:43,800 --> 00:29:45,507
This is a major disaster!

450
00:29:46,700 --> 00:29:48,179
You created me a Muslim...

451
00:29:48,267 --> 00:29:49,769
