the suspense today! Today?

453
00:29:54,133 --> 00:29:55,578
Fifty years after the event!

454
00:29:57,700 --> 00:29:59,577
Did You forget I am a Brahmin?
Here, look at this.

455
00:29:59,800 --> 00:30:01,711
Look at this!
A Brahmin.

456
00:30:03,967 --> 00:30:05,969
Yes, I've eaten eggs.

457
00:30:06,267 --> 00:30:07,541
I have eaten chickens
and so on.

458
00:30:07,600 --> 00:30:08,874
I have drunk liquor too.

459
00:30:09,100 --> 00:30:10,773
That... that's a hobby.

460
00:30:10,933 --> 00:30:12,776
I like that.
It's not what I was taught.

461
00:30:12,934 --> 00:30:14,379
My values were that of
a Brahmin.

462
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:17,575
But, this is a huge punishment!

463
00:30:18,167 --> 00:30:20,374
You've just gone ahead and
made me a Muslim!

464
00:30:20,967 --> 00:30:22,105
A Muslim!

465
00:30:23,367 --> 00:30:24,937
You could have made me
something else!

466
00:30:26,733 --> 00:30:27,871
God, listen to me.

467
00:30:29,267 --> 00:30:32,214
You just say that this is
all a dream, okay?

468
00:30:32,467 --> 00:30:34,811
But, I will atone for all the sins
I have committed!

469
00:30:34,900 --> 00:30:36,345
Here, take that!
That's for you.

470
00:30:36,900 --> 00:30:38,538
Alright?
Enough?

471
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:42,381
But, You are going
to say that this is a dream.

472
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:44,206
A bad dream.

473
00:30:44,900 --> 00:30:46,106
Alright?

474
00:30:47,767 --> 00:30:50,577
