484
00:31:46,767 --> 00:31:47,905
Punditji.

485
00:31:49,633 --> 00:31:53,513
If I am true, then why am I not
right?

486
00:31:54,700 --> 00:31:57,146
I don't get it.
Just explain it to me.

487
00:31:59,033 --> 00:32:00,740
What can I say to you?

488
00:32:02,967 --> 00:32:04,378
I am ruined.

489
00:32:05,233 --> 00:32:07,270
