someone else's door.

493
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:18,674
Oh, Lord!

494
00:32:18,767 --> 00:32:20,872
What kind of sinners
are being born, now?

495
00:32:21,567 --> 00:32:23,012
They don't spare young girls.

496
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:24,736
They hound the old ladies.

497
00:32:24,967 --> 00:32:27,277
And this is the limit!

498
00:32:27,967 --> 00:32:30,607
I mean, they didn't even spare
a man of your age! - What?

499
00:32:31,834 --> 00:32:34,246
