- No! You did the right thing.

500
00:32:34,600 --> 00:32:36,602
You have come to Lord Shiva.
Here's what I will do.

501
00:32:36,767 --> 00:32:38,678
I will go inside and
get a Panchmukhi Rudraksha.

502
00:32:38,767 --> 00:32:40,337
You have wear it around your neck.

503
00:32:40,400 --> 00:32:43,006
That will heal you and
set you right, too.

504
00:32:43,067 --> 00:32:44,808
I'll be right back.

505
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,577
Where is it?

506
00:32:50,800 --> 00:32:52,541
Indu? What are you looking for?

507
00:32:52,600 --> 00:32:54,443
Allah!
- What?

508
00:32:57,000 --> 00:33:00,174
