00:41:04,367 --> 00:41:06,005
Shraddha, don't get tense.

621
00:41:06,334 --> 00:41:08,177
I have found something, today...

622
00:41:08,234 --> 00:41:09,907
...which will put dad in
a good mood.

623
00:41:09,967 --> 00:41:12,243
