00:44:27,367 --> 00:44:28,573
Drink up.

687
00:44:28,634 --> 00:44:30,773
Mehmood Bhai? In Ahmadabad?

688
00:44:30,834 --> 00:44:32,905
I have a permit.
- In that case, cheers.

689
00:44:37,567 --> 00:44:38,637
What is it?

690
00:44:40,367 --> 00:44:42,210
Is this Scotch?
- Yes.

691
00:44:42,767 --> 00:44:44,508
It's orange flavored.

692
00:44:45,100 --> 00:44:47,637
I'll give you some that's lemon
flavored the next time you visit.

693
00:44:49,934 --> 00:44:51,504
Did you find out what happened?

694
00:44:53,034 --> 00:44:54,172
Your Muslim dad?

695
00:44:54,234 --> 00:44:56,942
Not my dad, my biological father.

696
00:44:57,034 --> 00:44:58,911
Okay, cool down!

697
00:44:59,200 --> 00:45:01,237
Let me tell you a story.

698
00:45:02,033 --> 00:45:03,376
Listen, Dharam Bhai.

699
00:45:04,234 --> 00:45:05,975
Your dad isn't...

700
00:45:06,334 --> 00:45:08,644
...what you think he is.

701
00:45:11,067 --> 00:45:12,478
