702
00:45:12,634 --> 00:45:15,410
I have a friend.
Dr. Farooque.

703
00:45:15,467 --> 00:45:17,777
Coincidentally,
he knows your father.

704
00:45:18,300 --> 00:45:20,837
He was telling me that
your father...

705
00:45:21,034 --> 00:45:23,947
...was admitted to his clinic
a couple of times.

706
00:45:24,600 --> 00:45:26,477
And according to Dr. Farooque...

707
00:45:26,867 --> 00:45:30,246
...your father is a very good man.

708
00:45:31,067 --> 00:45:33,570
When you were an infant...

709
00:45:34,300 --> 00:45:36,473
...your mother expired.

710
00:45:37,100 --> 00:45:40,570
In those days, your father
had a financial crisis at home.

711
00:45:41,567 --> 00:45:44,776
Later, he got hired
as a driver in Kuwait.

712
00:45:46,000 --> 00:45:48,742
