came back from Kuwait...

719
00:46:15,467 --> 00:46:18,311
...he found out about all this.

720
00:46:19,700 --> 00:46:22,476
God knows, how he felt
at that time.

721
00:46:23,367 --> 00:46:26,405
He went to the orphanage,
searching for you.

722
00:46:26,967 --> 00:46:30,847
But, Mr. Trivedi
had adopted you by then.

723
00:46:31,167 --> 00:46:34,580
The authorities didn't even tell
him who the adoptive parents were.

724
00:46:34,767 --> 00:46:36,713
He was really traumatized.

725
00:46:36,800 --> 00:46:41,010
