737
00:47:18,400 --> 00:47:21,904
No, brother, he told me that...

738
00:47:22,367 --> 00:47:25,177
I know. I understand
your feelings.

739
00:47:25,634 --> 00:47:27,113
Come on.
I will explain it.

740
00:47:27,467 --> 00:47:31,210
Now, Meer Shaukat Ali is over 80
by the grace of God.

741
00:47:31,300 --> 00:47:32,938
