00:47:38,534 --> 00:47:39,979
That's why I am saying that...

745
00:47:40,034 --> 00:47:42,036
That is what I am saying too,
brother.

746
00:47:42,734 --> 00:47:44,338
You see, a man who...

747
00:47:44,400 --> 00:47:47,244
...has lived his entire life
chanting the name of God...

748
00:47:47,700 --> 00:47:51,045
...and if he meets his only
son in the last days of his life...

749
00:47:51,100 --> 00:47:54,172
