00:48:06,600 --> 00:48:09,774
But, I would like you to meet
him in a way that...

756
00:48:09,867 --> 00:48:12,108
...he feels happy.

757
00:48:12,500 --> 00:48:13,945
He must not regret it.

758
00:48:14,033 --> 00:48:16,377
